{"tid":1779574,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蝙蝠俠汽油彈封面惹爭議 作者：對示威者用海報感高興 害怕人民表達政權遲早崩潰","createTime":"2019-12-11T18:26:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T23:31:22.000Z","uid":28765,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14344a3d3d8af9a17ea9f10917b1cf16a1ba166b","tid":1779574,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:26:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/20191211-22_8QCPs_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F20191211-22_8QCPs_1200x0.png&h=74c152a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n漫畫《蝙蝠俠：黑暗騎士歸來》的續集《The Golden Child》日前發表封面，顯示蝙蝠女手持汽油彈，並寫有「The Future is Young」字句，令人聯想到香港示威活動，並引起中國網民不滿。出版商 DC 事後將照片刪除，而圖片則被香港示威者廣泛使用。兩位漫畫創作人日前回應事件，解釋只是因為海報寫漏作者名而要下架，對香港示威者使用其作品感到高興，更明言害怕人民表達的政權遲早會崩潰。<br />\n<br />\n兩位漫畫創作人Frank Miller及Rafael Grampa周日在巴西出席一個漫畫節活動時，談及其海報引起的爭議。對於 DC 早前將海報下架，Grampa解釋只是因為該海報未有標明作者名稱。<br />\n<br />\n他又對香港示威者使用其海報及宣傳口號感到高興，「人們希望從中得到啟發，而他們正在為自己的自由而戰，這就是The Golden Child的意義」。<br />\n<br />\nMiller回應事件時說得更坦白：「有一些政治實體是如此害怕人民表達，甚至是害怕一張圖片&hellip;&hellip;反正它們遲早會崩潰。」<br />\n<br />\n出版商 DC 上月在 Instagram 上載了《The Golden Child》的封面，發現到蝙蝠女手持一個汽油彈，而且背景的粉紅大字寫上 「The Future is Young」（未來屬於年輕人）。有網民將封面與香港現況扣連，認為 DC 是要支持香港示威者。<br />\n<br />\n圖片上載後，大批中國網民都湧入去 DC 的 Instagram 批評做法，「你是腦癱還是怎麼的dc，你不想在中國混了？」又有網民質疑，為何蝙蝠俠會用上汽油彈作為武器，「蝙蝠俠拿燃燒瓶我真是頭一次見」。DC 隨即將照片刪除。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%9D%99%E8%9D%A0%E4%BF%A0%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2%E6%83%B9%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85-%E5%B0%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E8%88%88-%E5%AE%B3%E6%80%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%B2%E6%97%A9%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%259D%2599%25E8%259D%25A0%25E4%25BF%25A0%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2588%2588-%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E6%2580%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2581%25B2%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAJnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=dd8051a6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E8%259D%2599%25E8%259D%25A0%25E4%25BF%25A0%25E6%25B1%25BD%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25B0%2581%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%2583%25B9%25E7%2588%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B0-%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%2580%2585-%25E5%25B0%258D%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E5%25A8%2581%25E8%2580%2585%25E7%2594%25A8%25E6%25B5%25B7%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2584%259F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E8%2588%2588-%25E5%25AE%25B3%25E6%2580%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25AC%258A%25E9%2581%25B2%25E6%2597%25A9%25E5%25B4%25A9%25E6%25BD%25B0%2F&h=262fbe44\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E8%9D%99%E8%9D%A0%E4%BF%A0%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88%E5%B0%81%E9%9D%A2%E6%83%B9%E7%88%AD%E8%AD%B0-%E4%BD%9C%E8%80%85-%E5%B0%8D%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81%E8%80%85%E7%94%A8%E6%B5%B7%E5%A0%B1%E6%84%9F%E9%AB%98%E8%88%88-%E5%AE%B3%E6%80%95%E4%BA%BA%E6%B0%91%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%94%E6%94%BF%E6%AC%8A%E9%81%B2%E6%97%A9%E5%B4%A9%E6%BD%B0/</a>"},{"pid":"081635027411f5245d739c1900e6717d4ff2fdc7","tid":1779574,"uid":203797,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:42:28.000Z","msg":"「你不想在中國混了？」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好撚驚呀屌你老尾 <br />\n多謝佢地繼續做埋啲on9野搞臭支那個朵"},{"pid":"cc5117aa8911ca9c313d0f0f9bbd0160c4c2adde","tid":1779574,"uid":294221,"like":0